OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly mist and low cloud soon
OL,6,Fclearing. Then another dry day with
OL,7,Fsome good spells of sunshine, though
OL,8,Fmore cloud at times around Mull and
OL,9,FOban, and high cloud increasing
OL,10,Felsewhere later. Very warm.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA very warm and sunny evening
OL,13,Fwill be followed by a dry night with
OL,14,Fsome clear spells though sea fog may
OL,15,Fdrift in towards the Argyll Islands.
OL,16,FWinds remaining light.
OL,17,
OL,18,CFriday:FAnother dry day with some good
OL,19,Fspells of sunshine, though there could
OL,20,Fbe some mist and sea fog around the
OL,21,FArgyll Islands for a time. A hot day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
